{"id":7832,"date":"2017-10-22T15:06:48","date_gmt":"2017-10-22T08:06:48","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=7832"},"modified":"2020-07-23T09:11:39","modified_gmt":"2020-07-23T02:11:39","slug":"tang-toc-wordpress-voi-astra","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/astra\/tang-toc-wordpress-voi-astra","title":{"rendered":"T\u0103ng t\u1ed1c WordPress v\u1edbi Astra Theme"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">Astra sinh ra \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n <strong>t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c WordPress<\/strong>. M\u1ed9t theme \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sinh ra v\u1edbi s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh theme c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nhanh nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">50% Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Internet s\u1ebd c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1ecf trang n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t website c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian load h\u01a1n 3 gi\u00e2y.<\/p><cite>S\u01b0u t\u1ea7m<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c website l\u00e0 gia t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u1ea3m t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 tho\u00e1t trang v\u00e0 t\u0103ng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng, 2 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c quan tr\u1ecdng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n SEO ranking cho website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c WordPress<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Hosting ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/li><li>CDN cao c\u1ea5p<\/li><li>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh website \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u<\/li><li>Plugin nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/li><li>Cache t\u1ed1t<\/li><li>T\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n CSS, HTML, JavaScript<\/li><li>Kh\u00f4ng malware<\/li><li>Theme nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>\u1ede b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1edbi b\u1ea1n Astra theme. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Astra l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"539\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-1-1024x539.jpg\" alt=\"T\u0103ng t\u1ed1c WordPress ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn theme \u201cmi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed\u201d\" class=\"wp-image-7848\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-1.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-1-218x115.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-1-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-1-700x368.jpg 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-1-768x404.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/astratheme\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Astra<\/strong><\/a> l\u00e0 theme WordPress mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017 b\u1edfi <strong>Brainstorm Force<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft, <strong>Brainstorm Force<\/strong> l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u1ee9ng sau c\u00e1c plugin best-seller tr\u00ean <a href=\"\/out\/envato\" data-eafl-id=\"27490\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">Envato Market<\/a>. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 <em>Ultimate Addon for Visual Composer, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Ultimate Addon for Beaver Builder (opens in a new tab)