\u1ec3m tra page size, b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pingdom.com\/\">Pingdom<\/a>. Nh\u1edd page size si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 m\u00e0 Astra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 load trang v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i <strong>0.5s<\/strong> \u1edf giao di\u1ec7n m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng theme kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ed quy\u1ebft n\u00e0o gi\u00fap Astra c\u00f3 page size si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1edfi v\u00ec Astra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng Vanilla JavaScript (JavaScript thu\u1ea7n) ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi jQuery. Astra l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng theme ti\u00ean phong n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi jQuery hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111ang d\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Vanilla JavaScript v\u00ec tinh g\u1ecdn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. V\u1edbi JavaScript thu\u1ea7n, c\u00e1c developer s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm v\u1eefng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng&nbsp; JavaScript. M\u1ed7i d\u00f2ng code s\u1ebd ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a jQuery.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng l\u1ee3i \u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Nh\u1edd Vanilla JavaScript hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. Brainstorm Force \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. L\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u1ea3nh Raw, Astra theme \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 theme thu\u1ea7n, ch\u01b0a qua tinh ch\u1ec9nh v\u00e0 th\u00eam t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n ngay theme m\u00ec \u0103n li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i th\u00edch t\u1ef1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ho\u00e1 t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t theme website m\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng mong mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Astra l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tinh ch\u1ec9nh theme theo \u00fd c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 CSS, PHP, HTML c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u1edd l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecf c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap Astra tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>M\u1edf r\u1ed9ng tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh v\u1edbi Astra Pro<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n h\u01a1n cho vi\u1ec7c tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh theme, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/astrapro\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Astra Pro<\/strong>.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 plugin gi\u00fap Astra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t h\u00e0nh theme mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u00e1 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft c\u1ee7a plugin l\u00e0 <strong>$59\/n\u0103m<\/strong> hay <strong>$249 v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Astra Pro c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 hay kh\u00f4ng? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u xem<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Custom Layout &#8211; S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i c\u1ee7a Astra Pro<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Th\u00eam n\u1ed9i dung \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9u n\u01a1i n\u00e0o tr\u00ean website m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam Google Analytics tracking code, Google Tag Manager code, PHP code c\u1ee7a Advanced Custom Field, HTML code,&#8230; hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 CSS code \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Sidebar<\/li><li>Front Page<\/li><li>Blog Archive<\/li><li>Search Page<\/li><li>404 Page<\/li><li>hay to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 website.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Custom Layout c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Page Builder nh\u01b0 <strong><a href=\"\/out\/beaverbuilder\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Beaver Builder (opens in a new tab)\">Beaver Builder<\/a><\/strong>, <strong>Elementor<\/strong> ho\u1eb7c <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Brizy (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/brizypro\" target=\"_blank\">Brizy<\/a> <\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 th\u00eam n\u1ed9i dung. V\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t linh ho\u1ea1t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00e8n chi ti\u1ebft b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam \u1edf <a href=\"https:\/\/developers.wpastra.com\/theme-visual-hooks\/?_ga=2.72145555.1852404576.1539573076-1957640369.1537950228\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Astra Hook.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i cho c\u00e1c SaaS khi nh\u00fang m\u00e3 v\u00e0o website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n hay Iframe code.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"highlight\">\u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft SaaS l\u00e0 g\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft:&nbsp;<a href=\"\/wordpress\/saas-la-gi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SaaS l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao SaaS l\u1ea1i \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-image-11649\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"420\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Custom-Layout-Astra-Pro-1024x420.png\" alt=\"Custom Layout - Astra Pro\" class=\"wp-image-11649\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Custom-Layout-Astra-Pro-1024x420.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Custom-Layout-Astra-Pro-218x89.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Custom-Layout-Astra-Pro-300x123.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Custom-Layout-Astra-Pro-700x287.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Custom-Layout-Astra-Pro-768x315.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Custom-Layout-Astra-Pro.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Hook &#8211; B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00eam n\u1ed9i dung b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. Tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh Header v\u00e0 Footer n\u00e2ng cao<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Header<\/strong> v\u00e0 <strong>Footer<\/strong> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ef1c quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a website. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 menu hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng (<strong>Navigation<\/strong>).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Header c\u00f3 c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng sau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Sticky Header<\/strong>: C\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh header ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng xem ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed9i dung.<\/li><li><strong>Page Header<\/strong>: T\u1ea1o header ri\u00eang cho Page ho\u1eb7c Single Post.<\/li><li><strong>Transparent Header<\/strong>: T\u1ea1o header trong su\u1ed1t chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/li><li><strong>Header Section<\/strong>: Cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam 2 menu n\u1eb1m b\u00ean tr\u00ean ho\u1eb7c b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi menu ch\u00ednh.<\/li><li><strong>Retina Logo<\/strong>: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e9t cao cho c\u00e1c m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh 2k, 4k, 5k v\u00e0 Apple.<\/li><li><b>Mega Menu<\/b>: D\u1ea1ng menu t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay, cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o menu ph\u1ee5. Menu y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-11650 size-large\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"538\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Mega-menu-Astra-1024x538.jpg\" alt=\"Mega Menu\" class=\"wp-image-11650\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Mega-menu-Astra.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Mega-menu-Astra-218x115.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Mega-menu-Astra-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Mega-menu-Astra-700x368.jpg 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Mega-menu-Astra-768x404.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Mega Menu &#8211; M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Footer h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 chia Layout ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u1ea3nh background v\u00e0 font cho Footer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-image-11652\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"594\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/footer-widget-colors-1024x594.png\" alt=\"Footer Astra v\u1edbi font\" class=\"wp-image-11652\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/footer-widget-colors-1024x594.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/footer-widget-colors-218x126.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/footer-widget-colors-300x174.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/footer-widget-colors-700x406.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/footer-widget-colors-768x445.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/footer-widget-colors.png 1238w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Background Image v\u00e0 Typography<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. T\u1ea1o website b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi WooComerce &amp; Astra Pro &amp; Page Builder<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"733\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Woocommerce-Astra-1024x733.gif\" alt=\"Astra v\u00e0 WooCommerce\" class=\"wp-image-11655\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Woocommerce-Astra-1024x733.gif 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Woocommerce-Astra-218x156.gif 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Woocommerce-Astra-300x215.gif 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Woocommerce-Astra-700x501.gif 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Woocommerce-Astra-768x550.gif 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Astra Pro h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t WooCommerce. Khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Beaver Builder hay Elementor s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o website b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Astra Pro cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o Layout, style, b\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng zoom \u1ea3nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. T\u1ea1o website b\u00e1n kho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi Astra Pro<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t WooCommerce, Astra Pro c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 LearnDash v\u00e0 LifterLMS \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o website b\u00e1n kho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image wp-image-11656 size-large\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"548\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Learndash-1024x548.png\" alt=\"Learndash Astra Pro\" class=\"wp-image-11656\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Learndash.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Learndash-218x117.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Learndash-300x161.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Learndash-700x375.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Learndash-768x411.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Learn Dash<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. Tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh Typography, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i kh\u00e1c<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"503\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-Pro-1024x503.png\" alt=\"T\u0103ng t\u1ed1c wordpress v\u1edbi Astra\" class=\"wp-image-11653\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-Pro-1024x503.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-Pro-218x107.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-Pro-300x147.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-Pro-700x344.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-Pro-768x377.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Astra-Pro.png 1276w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n font c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n website v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Astra \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n Google Font.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 <strong>White Label<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra theme ri\u00eang v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh b\u1ea1n. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng Astra Pro.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Astra l\u00e0 theme thu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c WordPress \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Astra Pro b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o website b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, website b\u00e1n kho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh theme chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Astra c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o Forum v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a <strong>bbPress<\/strong> v\u00e0 <strong>BuddyPress<\/strong>. \u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n Astra b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y xem t\u1ea1i <a href=\"https:\/\/trello.com\/b\/yEXMkrzZ\/astra-public-roadmap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Astra Public Roadmap<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u theme Astra, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c Wordpress website \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf xung \u0111\u1ed9t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c Page Builder y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":9188,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[37],"tags":[